<br>
How many of ya that are arguing back and forth about blowin the ever-livin shit outta some country/person, etc... have ever been in the military?<br>
<br>
How many of ya have held a gun in ya hands that can take the head completely off of a persons' shoulders? How many of ya have seen that happen?<br>
<br>
